The evidence with the title 'Why we care about privacy - Markkula Center for applied ethics ' says Jun 1, 2012  ... People can be harmed or debilitated if there is no restriction on the public 's access to and use of personal information .  ... Financial records -- whether from banks, credit bureaus or the IRS--welfare records, sites visited on the Internet and a variety of other sources hold many intimate details of a person 's life. 
